&lt;blockquote&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;T&amp;ocirc; come&amp;ccedil;ando a encontrar (&lt;a href=&quot;http://cfpub.epa.gov/ncer_abstracts/index.cfm/fuseaction/display.abstractDetail/abstract/8085/report/F/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.los-gatos.ca.us/davidbu/pedgen.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;2&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.pedalpowergenerator.com/PPG-12-200-nc25a-charge-controller.htm&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;3&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.futurespark.com.au/schools-information&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;4&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.christoph-thetard.de/christoph-thetard.de/R2B2_3-engl.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;5&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.ecofriend.com/entry/amazing-diy-projects-to-create-electricity-at-home/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;6&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.energybulletin.net/stories/2011-06-01/bike-powered-electricity-generators-are-not-sustainable&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;7&lt;/a&gt;)... Mandei errado o link do &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.ecofriend.com/entry/amazing-diy-projects-to-create-electricity-at-home/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;ecofriends&lt;/a&gt; mas deu numa p&amp;aacute;gina que tem outros projetos interessantes pra quem n&amp;atilde;o conhece.&lt;/p&gt;
